  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Add the <strong>linguine</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong>&nbsp;and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Cook the <strong>linguine</strong> for 8-10 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p>\r\n<p>Once done, drain the <strong>linguine</strong> and return it to the pot</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cavolo-nero-linguine-with-fiery-goats-cheese/step-1.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, reboil a kettle</p>\r\n<p>Roughly chop the <strong>cavolo nero</strong></p>",
      "order": 2,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cavolo-nero-linguine-with-fiery-goats-cheese/step-2.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped cavolo nero</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p>\r\n<p>Cook the <strong>cavolo nero</strong> for 5-6 min Once done, drain the cavolo nero</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cavolo-nero-linguine-with-fiery-goats-cheese/step-3.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, roll the <strong>goats' cheese log<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> over the <strong>dried chilli flakes</strong> until fully coated</p>\r\n<p>Cut the <strong>chilli goats&rsquo; cheese</strong> into slices (or break it up into rough pieces) and set aside</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cavolo-nero-linguine-with-fiery-goats-cheese/step-4.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Grate the <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p>\r\n<p>Peel and chop the <strong>garlic</strong> roughly</p>\r\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock cube<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> in 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[100ml]</span>&nbsp;<strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cavolo-nero-linguine-with-fiery-goats-cheese/step-5.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>whole almonds</strong>, <strong>drained cavolo nero</strong>, <strong>grated cheddar</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and a very generous drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong></p>\r\n<p>Blitz for 2 min or until a smooth sauce remains &ndash; this is your <strong>cavolo nero pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cavolo-nero-linguine-with-fiery-goats-cheese/step-6.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>cavolo nero pesto</strong> to the <strong>drained linguine</strong> and give everything a good old mix up &ndash; this is your <strong>green linguine</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "image": "/images/instructions/cavolo-nero-linguine-with-fiery-goats-cheese/step-7.jpg"
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> green linguine</strong> topped with the <strong>chilli goats&rsquo; cheese </strong></p>\r\n<p>Drizzle with some<strong> olive oil</strong> and a generous grind of<strong>&nbsp;black pepper</strong></p>\r\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8
    }
  ],
